data.description: Waterfront Deeded Property!! This 4 bedroom. 2.5 bathroom home features hardwood floors, granite countertops, large separate dining room, breakfast area. Primary suite has an amazing view of the water and French doors leading out onto the deck. Exterior features include large deck that you can entertain on or just sit and enjoy your beautiful surroundings. There is a secondary guest suite that has views of the water, its own bathroom and access to the deck. There is a floating dock, sand area for lounging in the sun, and a large detached garage on a separate lot. Enjoy seasonal native flowers & plants to the area planted throughout the yard and so much more. Ask how you can receive up to $1500 credit by using one of our preferred lenders. Seller is offering to pay up to 3% towards purchaser's closing cost. Exclusions may apply.
